		{
			"text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 42 for SLE 12 SP3)",
			"title": "Topic",
			"type": "Summary"
		},
		{
			"text": "This update for the Linux Kernel 4.4.180-94_153 fixes one issue.\n\nThe following security issue was fixed:\n\n- CVE-2022-0492: Fixed a privilege escalation related to cgroups v1 release_agent feature, which allowed bypassing namespace isolation unexpectedly (bsc#1195543).\n",
			"title": "Details",
			"type": "General"
